# Route engine (scoped)

Preserve pipeline: validation → candidates → hard/soft filters → scoring → assembly → fallback → warnings.

- Do not silently drop places, relax filters, or trim stops without warnings/debug.
- Separate hard vs soft filter removals; expose counts in debug/admin paths.
- Low-value categories and non-route-eligible places must not enter tourist routes unless explicit.
- Partial tail rebuild for live edit — do not full-rebuild when tail-only is enough.

Key files: `services/candidate_retrieval_service.py`, `services/route_builder_v2_service.py`, `services/route_eligibility.py`.

Full pipeline notes: `docs/` and `AGENTS.md` when debugging complex route loss.
